{"tid":969950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要點先可以滿足阿牛，郭紹傑呢班撚屌？","createTime":"2019-01-05T12:16:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T14:09:39.000Z","uid":37528,"like":112,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"08b07722bc4a5d2b0817d01e33e0bdf3ef567dae","tid":969950,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T12:16:03.000Z","msg":"日本道歉左咁撚多次，而家仲好死到話人無道歉<br />\n你係要屌人，好心都撚過其他point<br />\n<br />\n仲有自己犯左法，走去屌9日本政府拉人，話人迫害？<br />\n有無咁撚智障呀？<br />\n呢班撚屌根本係貪得無厭，為屌而屌<br />\n影撚衰香港人<br />\n<br />\n幾時可以係中環ifc外面加埋郭紹傑同嚴敏華落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果有人識日本既朋友，麻煩話俾佢地知香港好多人都支持日本嚴正執法<br />\n<br />\n呢班人真係好撚核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e82c70b7670fc1cf91fb3346ba0c7ccea191072b","tid":969950,"uid":37528,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T12:16:45.000Z","msg":"陶傑幾時邀請阿牛上光明頂呀"},{"pid":"a4268a24e4d68b3fa81570fd33098230a66fca54","tid":969950,"uid":20898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T12:19:02.000Z","msg":"返支那世界之娼個日本鎮度擴議"},{"pid":"c65ad6c1b8eb94a667a7a54460e48ba48644f22d","tid":969950,"uid":52459,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T12:31:04.000Z","msg":"保釣同環保一樣，都一門生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95934c8c8e8204520d77d42c649b3cce9d717f0e","tid":969950,"uid":79563,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T13:06:30.000Z","msg":"日本仔請佢地飲sake, 醉左就唔嘈啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.japantimes.2xx.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/p20-gordenker-wth-a-20150726-870x697.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.japantimes.2xx.jp%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F07%2Fp20-gordenker-wth-a-20150726-870x697.jpg&h=9c2f858d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4ef3d2cd5ee7560243523ea828a4ca80c9945f2","tid":969950,"uid":81424,"like